Package: riesztree
Type: Package
Title: Single-Tree Backend for Riesz Regression
Version: 0.0.1
Authors@R: person("Alejandro", "Schuler", role = c("aut", "cre"), email = "alejandro.schuler@berkeley.edu")
Description: R wrapper around the Python 'riesztree' package. Fits a single
    decision tree to estimate the Riesz representer of a linear functional
    via greedy splits on the augmented Bregman-Riesz loss. Subclass of
    'rieszreg::RieszEstimatorR6'.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
Imports:
    R6,
    reticulate,
    rieszreg
Suggests:
    testthat (>= 3.0.0),
    pkgload
Config/testthat/edition: 3
RoxygenNote: 7.3.0
